<A HREF="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/recipesearch.html?tradeskill=Tailoring" TARGET="_BLANK">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/recipesearch.html?tradeskill=Tailoring</A>

that has all the recipes for tailoring, in case you didnt have them already. to me, the only challenging part would be getting the rockhopper pelts, which even to a 56 bst can get a little annoying, seeing as how they occasionally blind me (about 1/100 though). you also will probably have to do multiple tradeskills to make the armor if your friends arent training smithing and brewing for the other materials you need. also, good luck getting the armor at lvl 30, the hoppers are pretty tough to kill, even with a group. your best bet would be to concentrate on making wu's armor, which will get you some nice gear, considering your making it yourself, as well as major TS increase. hope this info helps you, good luck!

